  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/1373a9b27db382dbc166ff88516438e6.poster.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/1373a9b27db382dbc166ff88516438e6.webm?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/1373a9b27db382dbc166ff88516438e6.mp4?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/8f85cb50f0b7299b6d7bd5aa74c9cfec.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are Nerobi, a small spirit with enormous potential. Your memories and powers have vanished following an epic battle. You find yourself in the Middle World, which you must travel to discover your past, recover your powers, and save the future of the 4 Worlds.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/741b96b2b112bf22a1ff60c123a3ac95.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/8f85cb50f0b7299b6d7bd5aa74c9cfec.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PUZZLES & PLATFORMING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coordinate, jump, avoid obstacles, solve puzzles and riddles in this harsh but fair platform game. Crossing the Middle World is no joke: try it and see for yourself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AN IMMERSIVE WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome in a world entirely hand-drawn and animated frame by frame, ready to be explored and populated by strange characters, while an emotional soundtrack lulls you along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/f164937ff7537fbdf3b880e4b608ea9f.poster.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/f164937ff7537fbdf3b880e4b608ea9f.webm?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/f164937ff7537fbdf3b880e4b608ea9f.mp4?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RECOVER YOUR POWERS AND MEMORIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move forward to rediscover memories and powers that will gradually enrich the gameplay and open up new areas of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/d35303e288f2d8f51ac09d2ad7c96f64.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=304 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLEASH YOUR WRATH!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For most of your adventure, you won't be able to fight. But there will be moments when the presence of Demons will trigger you... and then you'll be able to kick their asses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0a72773ec3fc65207c43af8ae3f65d4d.poster.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0a72773ec3fc65207c43af8ae3f65d4d.webm?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0a72773ec3fc65207c43af8ae3f65d4d.mp4?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/8f85cb50f0b7299b6d7bd5aa74c9cfec.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=64 /></span> <strong></strong><br><strong>RUINS AND COLLECTIBLE CARDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover all the Ruins to reconstruct the game's lore. Explore every corner of the Middle World to find Cards that will reveal details about the Characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0416ff664b24d8bb4f91f9f9a80c295a.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=359 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/1373a9b27db382dbc166ff88516438e6.poster.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/1373a9b27db382dbc166ff88516438e6.webm?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/1373a9b27db382dbc166ff88516438e6.mp4?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/8f85cb50f0b7299b6d7bd5aa74c9cfec.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are Nerobi, a small spirit with enormous potential. Your memories and powers have vanished following an epic battle. You find yourself in the Middle World, which you must travel to discover your past, recover your powers, and save the future of the 4 Worlds.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/741b96b2b112bf22a1ff60c123a3ac95.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/8f85cb50f0b7299b6d7bd5aa74c9cfec.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PUZZLES & PLATFORMING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coordinate, jump, avoid obstacles, solve puzzles and riddles in this harsh but fair platform game. Crossing the Middle World is no joke: try it and see for yourself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AN IMMERSIVE WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome in a world entirely hand-drawn and animated frame by frame, ready to be explored and populated by strange characters, while an emotional soundtrack lulls you along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/f164937ff7537fbdf3b880e4b608ea9f.poster.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/f164937ff7537fbdf3b880e4b608ea9f.webm?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/f164937ff7537fbdf3b880e4b608ea9f.mp4?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RECOVER YOUR POWERS AND MEMORIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move forward to rediscover memories and powers that will gradually enrich the gameplay and open up new areas of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/d35303e288f2d8f51ac09d2ad7c96f64.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=304 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLEASH YOUR WRATH!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For most of your adventure, you won't be able to fight. But there will be moments when the presence of Demons will trigger you... and then you'll be able to kick their asses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0a72773ec3fc65207c43af8ae3f65d4d.poster.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0a72773ec3fc65207c43af8ae3f65d4d.webm?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0a72773ec3fc65207c43af8ae3f65d4d.mp4?t=1773233665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/8f85cb50f0b7299b6d7bd5aa74c9cfec.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=64 /></span> <strong></strong><br><strong>RUINS AND COLLECTIBLE CARDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover all the Ruins to reconstruct the game's lore. Explore every corner of the Middle World to find Cards that will reveal details about the Characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534250/extras/0416ff664b24d8bb4f91f9f9a80c295a.avif?t=1773233665\" width=600 height=359 /></span></p>",
